            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Safinius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Sabellio pater </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> I]uli[o</del> <lb n="2"/><del rend="erasure">Ph<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>l<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>p[po</del>] <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure">Caesari</del> <lb n="4"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>o<supplied reason="lost">bilis</supplied>s[imo</del>] <lb n="5"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">fi</supplied>l<supplied reason="lost">io</supplied> I<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>mp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan></supplied> C<supplied reason="lost">ae</supplied><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan></del> <lb n="6"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan></supplied> I[uli</del>] <lb n="7"/><del rend="erasure">[Philippi Pii</del>] <lb n="8"/>Felicis <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>Aquileienses <lb n="10"/>devoti <expan><abbr>numin</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>maiestatiq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> eius
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Erhalten ist der Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Der Stein wurde in der Antike wiederverwendet. Angaben beziehen sich auf die jüngere Inschrift (CIL V 8971); auf der Oberseite Grabinschrift der späten Republik (CIL V 8981 a).</p>
            </div>
